Samuel Hancock & Arthur Moseley,
Junr., 22 Feb. 1724, & conveyed to sd.
Locket by deeds ack’d. in Henrico Co,
Ct. :

JOHN CARRELL, 300 acs. (N. L.),
Bruonsuick Co; §. side of Maherin Riv;
beg, adj, George Walton, near head of
the Falling. Run; Adam Sims; & Chapman's land; near the road to Christiana;
