COL. HENRY HARRISON, ESQR.,
of Surry Co; 1888 acs. (N. L.), Brunswick Co; on both sides the Great Creek;
adj. Charles Lucas; on the Indian Line;
on Rose’s Cr; 28 Sept, 1732, p, 534.
9 Lbs., 10 Shill.
